\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14485215\charrsid16603783  it back, me great grandfather's brother was supposed to have mon
ey and land in Ireland under the name of Michael Shannon. Now me grandfather says, well, he says there's only one to go after that and he called me father Michael - Michael Edward see. So of course the tradition went on and it was supposed to have come ov
er from Ireland to England and stayed here a while and then went back again. So when he went back again to Ireland me - he died there so me grandfather went to Ireland to see him buried and they wanted him to - you know, to take the will and all the }{
