\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1853741 MS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14485215\charrsid16603783 
In the - in the early part he was - Secretary of what is now the Transport and General Workers but the - in those days the union was the Tramway and Vehicle Workers Union. He was Secretary of that at one 
time but - anyhow - how long it was I don't know. He lost that job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4129778 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14485215\charrsid16603783 Did he used to stay in a lot your father or not?
